<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hear n Heal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="assets/logo.png" alt="Hear n Heal Logo" class="logo-img">
            <span class="logo-text">Hear n Heal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">HOME</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">MODULES</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">BOOKING</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">TESTIMONIALS</a>
            <a href="#" class="login-btn">Login / Signup</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="hero">
        <div class="image-card card-left">
            <img src="assets/meditation.png" alt="Meditation on Clouds">
        </div>

        <section class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">Hear &<br>Heal</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">
                A digital sanctuary bridging the gap between<br>
                <em>modern anxiety</em> and <em>holistic frequency healing</em>.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-btn">
                Book your Session
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M5 12H19" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M12 5L19 12L12 19" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </section>

        <div class="image-card card-right">
            <img src="assets/beach.png" alt="Tropical Beach">
        </div>
    </main>

    <section class="anxiety-section">
        <div class="anxiety-content">
            <h2 class="anxiety-title scroll-reveal">The Epidemic of<br><em>"High-Functioning Anxiety"</em></h2>
            <p class="anxiety-description scroll-reveal">
                Modern society creates a disconnect. We are overwhelmed by fast-paced lifestyles, demanding careers, and
                academic pressure, leaving us silently exhausted.
            </p>

            <div class="feature-list scroll-reveal">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Accessibility Gap</h3>
                    <p class="feature-text">Traditional holistic healing is often geographically or financially out of
                        reach.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Mental Fatigue</h3>
                    <p class="feature-text">Students face exam paralysis; Professionals suffer from invisible burnout.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="anxiety-image-container scroll-reveal">
            <div class="polaroid-large">
                <img src="assets/anxiety-view.png" alt="Person looking at mountains" loading="lazy">
                <div class="tag-pill">Emotional State</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials-section">
        <h2 class="section-title scroll-reveal">Healing <em>Stories</em></h2>

        <div class="testimonials-container scroll-reveal">
            <!-- Card 1 (Dark) -->
            <div class="testimonial-card dark">
                <div class="profile-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Michael Ross" loading="lazy">
                    <span class="name-pill">Michael</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"As a CEO, I'm emotionally drained and time-poor. The deep focus tools here are a game
                    changer for my mental clarity."</p>
                <div class="author-info">
                    <h4>Michael Ross</h4>
                    <span>TECH FOUNDER</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 (Light/Active) -->
            <div class="testimonial-card light">
                <div class="profile-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Sarah Jenkins" loading="lazy">
                </div>
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"I was overwhelmed by exam anxiety and peer pressure. Hear n Heal gave me the quick
                    relief I needed to sleep again."</p>
                <div class="author-info">
                    <h4>Sarah Jenkins</h4>
                    <span>UNIVERSITY STUDENT</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 (Dark/Duplicate for visual balance) -->
            <div class="testimonial-card dark">
                <div class="profile-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Michael Ross" loading="lazy">
                    <span class="name-pill">Michael</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"As a CEO, I'm emotionally drained and time-poor. The deep focus tools here are a game
                    changer for my mental clarity."</p>
                <div class="author-info">
                    <h4>Michael Ross</h4>
                    <span>TECH FOUNDER</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
                entries.forEach(entry => {
                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                        entry.target.classList.add('active');
                    }
                });
            }, {
                threshold: 0.2,
                rootMargin: "0px"
            });

            document.querySelectorAll('.scroll-reveal').forEach((el) => {
                observer.observe(el);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>